{"tid":687704,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【M巾盤戰場】兩幫代理大打出手 串演Street Fighter拳拳到肉","createTime":"2018-06-02T13:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T14:52:27.000Z","uid":83582,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"bd84d241bc71694439cf2c7aad2bda54be931a9e","tid":687704,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:10:30.000Z","msg":"2018年06月02日 <br />\n<br />\n 高溫之下，地產代理都零舍躁底！恒地（012）大角嘴割房盤利奧坊．凱岸於國際金融中心(ifc)設置示位，繼有代理反罵客之後，又有數名代理疑因撈客問題起爭執，出現互毆場面，猶如真人「街霸」上演。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳一條長51秒的短片顯示，數名代理正出手互毆，有兩名保安嘗試分開，並一直大喊「停手！停手！」，但不果。而周邊旁觀者一直起哄，不斷發出「Woo、打呀」等聲音，甚至有嘻笑聱，令現場氣氛進一步緊張。<br />\n<br />\n未幾一位代理失足跘倒地上，其後3至4名代理乘勝追擊，如踢波一樣不斷用腳起勢踢向倒地者的背部。經過一輪糾纏後，一名代理打得興起，覺得拳頭都未能渲洩心中不滿，便隨手拿起欄杆座，並揮向倒地者背部。兩批人最後終被分開，不過一名摺起手袖的代理明顯仍感憤怒，一手拿着欄杆座，用「殺死人」的氣勢向敵方大叫「你講多次！」<br />\n<br />\n據稱，事後已有人報警處理，同時有救護員到場為傷者驗傷。市場消息指，兩批代理分屬世紀21及香港置業。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180602/large/1527937000_46a1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180602%2Flarge%2F1527937000_46a1.jpg&h=9768043f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180602/58269931\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F58269931&d=MByN8l5tr7paOzoQpA3Ku10Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=e7599a5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180602%2F58269931&h=ff0cf99e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180602/58269931</a>"},{"pid":"7ad323b22392c47052ba59f7d9fb48607f1800fb","tid":687704,"uid":83582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:13:03.000Z","msg":"AA狗成班爛仔, 日日都出事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29613350a26bb5c16c8ecfcd84f20d379b870b30","tid":687704,"uid":29625,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:17:04.000Z","msg":"往死裡打"},{"pid":"852dfdfe5c1d1cc634562946d969b82b4c80cf8b","tid":687704,"uid":25641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:36:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d67faec9083891963bcbefefbb469ac40bff291","tid":687704,"uid":71441,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:42:00.000Z","msg":"灰衫唔錯，其他係度hea, 推下推下咁"},{"pid":"37ba4116204b5ebf76f8d56aea9e7ea496ee9943","tid":687704,"uid":29773,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:45:34.000Z","msg":"次次都係赤手空拳<br />\n有冇悶D<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2498d96f3ffa15ee40b9dbff5194c0b1d1ee66e2","tid":687704,"uid":74778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T13:50:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/02/215002_aac15dddd98c71d8cd9808d91163740f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F02%2F215002_aac15dddd98c71d8cd9808d91163740f.png&h=dd48a630&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"faf4e776a4345b1dd6f6b2cab3d5683bc687c792","tid":687704,"uid":107470,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:05:57.000Z","msg":"成班廢柴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買樓都唔會搵呢d企街廢物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8999cb806f0da1854480b637bbba516cfa715cbe","tid":687704,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T14:39:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b068d901ec564e5d6654e602edf14ce03a85a1df","tid":687704,"uid":159392,"like":1,"dis